# Docking Compartment

A docking compartment is a module of a space station to which visiting spacecraft can dock. Docking Compartment may refer to:
* Docking Compartment 1 (Pirs)
* Docking Compartment 2 (Poisk)
See also
* Mini-Research Modules
* Mir Docking Module
